    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Pedinotus dispar sp. nov. (A, C–J—female, holotype; B—male, paratype). A, B, Habitus, dorsal view. C, Head, front view. D, Head, dorsal view. E, Head, lateral view. F, Basal segments of antenna. G, Mesosoma, dorsal view. H, Mesosoma, lateral view. I, Hind femur and tibia, lateral view. J, Propodeum and first-third metasomal tergites, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10090938/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10090940>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Pedinotus dispar sp. nov. (A–C—female, holotype; D—male, paratype). A, Wings. B, Metasoma, lateral view. C, D, Metasoma, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10090940/files/figure.png" ;
